overview: In this original comedy, the world is flipped. Most people are gay and the way of the world is much happier, until one man decides he is going to come out of the closet straight by professing his love to a woman. Let the claw ripping begin. The story goes on a wild and wacky ride as we look into the world of carnal urges and restriction all wrapped in an all American package.
title: I'm Coming Out
